    "Classification of NER methods.",
    "Fig. 4.4Fig.",
    "A typical architecture for deep learning NER methods.",
    "Recent advancements in NER have seen diverse methodological innovations.Li et al. (2022) conducted a comprehensive survey highlighting the evolution of deep learning techniques in NER, providing a foundation for contemporary research[32].Wang et al.",
    "(2022) introduced MINER, addressing out-of-vocabulary entity recognition through information-theoretic principles, while their kNN-NER leveraged nearest neighbour search to enhance contextual similarity modelling[33]."
